# describe needed things to build up a whole AI system from beginning


- core hardware for AI application (GPU, CPU... etc)
- a cloud system aka cluster for running. eg: https://kubernetes.io/
- specific AI applications including backend and frontend application
  - backend application will run on servers hosted on cloud eg: Pods on Kuberneste
  - frontend application running on any web hosts, smart phone, robot that calls backend application on cloud via internet connection

- training data 
